{"id":76,"date":"2024-12-04T10:45:44","date_gmt":"2024-12-04T10:45:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/brookcottage.me\/?page_id=76"},"modified":"2025-08-24T12:57:21","modified_gmt":"2025-08-24T12:57:21","slug":"welcome-to-brook-cottage","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/brookcottage.me\/","title":{"rendered":"Welcome to Brook Cottage"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-created_by=\"avia_inline_auto\" id=\"style-css-av-1yptc-280ee19ac312e10586b0fda418e1d5e2\">\n.avia-section.av-1yptc-280ee19ac312e10586b0fda418e1d5e2{\nbackground-color:#6e7a69;\nbackground-image:unset;\n}\n<\/style>\n<div id='av_section_1'  class='avia-section av-1yptc-280ee19ac312e10586b0fda418e1d5e2 header_color avia-section-small avia-no-border-styling  avia-builder-el-0  el_before_av_slideshow_full  avia-builder-el-first  avia-bg-style-scroll container_wrap fullsize'  ><div class='container av-section-cont-open' ><main  role=\"main\" itemprop=\"mainContentOfPage\"  class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-76'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>\n<div  class='flex_column av-1pa2s-92d7d27926e26cadf0a93b1984e8334b av_one_full  avia-builder-el-1  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  first flex_column_div  '     ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-m49ri271-ba87cf565356f40d4c10b185f9b4b3af '   itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop=\"text\" ><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Welcome to Brook Cottage Camping<\/h1>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div>\n\n<\/div><\/div><\/main><!-- close content main element --><\/div><\/div><div id='full_slider_1'  class='avia-fullwidth-slider main_color avia-shadow av-desktop-hide av-medium-hide av-small-hide av-mini-hide  avia-builder-el-3  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_section   slider-not-first container_wrap fullsize'  ><div  class='avia-slideshow av-m49rqkkv-5f94321c1795a873bba845b69fa72207 avia-slideshow-no scaling av_slideshow_full avia-slide-slider av-desktop-hide av-medium-hide av-small-hide av-mini-hide av-slideshow-ui av-control-default av-slideshow-manual av-loop-once av-loop-manual-endless   avia-slideshow-1' data-slideshow-options=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;loop_autoplay&quot;:&quot;once&quot;,&quot;interval&quot;:5,&quot;loop_manual&quot;:&quot;manual-endless&quot;,&quot;autoplay_stopper&quot;:false,&quot;noNavigation&quot;:false,&quot;bg_slider&quot;:false,&quot;keep_padding&quot;:false,&quot;hoverpause&quot;:false,&quot;show_slide_delay&quot;:0}\"  itemprop=\"image\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/ImageObject\" ><ul class='avia-slideshow-inner ' ><\/ul><\/div><\/div>\n<div id='av_section_2'  class='avia-section av-157us-02d49070777c1d59f6da9bf5723f2dd6 main_color avia-section-small avia-no-border-styling  avia-builder-el-4  el_after_av_slideshow_full  el_before_av_section  avia-bg-style-scroll container_wrap fullsize'  ><div class='container av-section-cont-open' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-76'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>\n<div  class='flex_column av-253oc-db9cc502c46c8daf7f0ebb421a0e4fe2 av_one_full  avia-builder-el-5  el_before_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-first  first flex_column_div  '     ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-m49rt7k2-a2a54cc7ad4755ac0d9d3c6eea2f17d5 '   itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop=\"text\" ><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Tranquil, intimate spot on a working farm amid the County Down drumlins<\/h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Just a 10\u2011minute drive to Drumkeeragh Forest and 30 minutes from Belfast<\/h2>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Shops and dining in Ballynahinch are only a 15\u2011minute drive away<\/h2>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div><div  class='flex_column av-1ko6k-0a5219b478aa1c1da9dfc9f6ac8b0ff9 av_one_half  avia-builder-el-7  el_after_av_one_full  el_before_av_one_half  first flex_column_div  column-top-margin'     ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-m49rti1k-9aaaa125517420c5434913943a108207 '   itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop=\"text\" ><p><strong>Craving peace near forests, beaches, and city life? Brook Cottage Camping nestled in the gentle drumlins of County Down is your perfect retreat. You\u2019re only a 10-minute drive from Drumkeeragh Forest\u2014ideal for scenic walks\u2014and just thirty minutes from Belfast, Northern Ireland\u2019s vibrant capital.<\/p>\n<p><\/strong>The small, family-friendly camping area is a pop-up site set on a working farm, offering portable toilets and a washing-up spot. Situated on a quiet country lane, you won\u2019t have much traffic noise, yet it\u2019s easy to head off for day trips to Northern Ireland\u2019s top attractions.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div><div  class='flex_column av-tark-1aaf079d04930a82b79b8e64bed05379 av_one_half  avia-builder-el-9  el_after_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-last  flex_column_div  column-top-margin'     ><section  class='av_textblock_section av-m49rtrfl-9f5619bf247ad28b0026ae1efc96331a '   itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/CreativeWork\" ><div class='avia_textblock'  itemprop=\"text\" ><p>Grab your fishing gear and hit one of the nearby lakes\u2014just a 15-minute drive away\u2014or stock up on provisions in the market town of Ballynahinch, with all the shops and eateries you\u2019d expect.<\/p>\n<p>In a 20-minute drive through Dromara and Finnis you\u2019ll reach Slieve Croob, the birthplace of the River Lagan. After your climb, you\u2019ll be treated to expansive views. And if you fancy an indoor treat afterward, Lisburn, 25 minutes away, has a pool with slides, a cinema, and bowling.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/section><\/div>\n\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><!-- close content main div --><\/div><\/div>\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-created_by=\"avia_inline_auto\" id=\"style-css-av-1p2o4-420bf0d8f1f11e605fd4319b4ce79aa4\">\n.avia-section.av-1p2o4-420bf0d8f1f11e605fd4319b4ce79aa4{\nbackground-color:#edebe6;\nbackground-image:unset;\n}\n<\/style>\n<div id='av_section_3'  class='avia-section av-1p2o4-420bf0d8f1f11e605fd4319b4ce79aa4 main_color avia-section-small avia-no-border-styling  avia-builder-el-11  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_section  avia-bg-style-scroll container_wrap fullsize'  ><div class='container av-section-cont-open' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-76'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>\n\n<style type=\"text\/css\" data-created_by=\"avia_inline_auto\" id=\"style-css-av-mepp0l4w-4fb2c2d10e1c23576f61b03b6cdbd0ba\">\n.avia-image-container.av-mepp0l4w-4fb2c2d10e1c23576f61b03b6cdbd0ba img.avia_image{\nbox-shadow:none;\n}\n.avia-image-container.av-mepp0l4w-4fb2c2d10e1c23576f61b03b6cdbd0ba .av-image-caption-overlay-center{\ncolor:#ffffff;\n}\n<\/style>\n<div  class='avia-image-container av-mepp0l4w-4fb2c2d10e1c23576f61b03b6cdbd0ba av-styling- avia-align-center  avia-builder-el-12  el_before_av_one_full  avia-builder-el-first '   itemprop=\"image\" itemscope=\"itemscope\" itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/ImageObject\" ><div class=\"avia-image-container-inner\"><div class=\"avia-image-overlay-wrap\"><img decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class='wp-image-118 avia-img-lazy-loading-not-118 avia_image ' src=\"https:\/\/brookcottage.me\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/pic-1.jpg\" alt='' title='pic (1)'  height=\"749\" width=\"999\"  itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" srcset=\"https:\/\/brookcottage.me\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/pic-1.jpg 999w, https:\/\/brookcottage.me\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/pic-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/brookcottage.me\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/pic